               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Dǝrsanä sanbata krǝstiyān “Homily on the Sabbath of Christians”
                     (Homily on the observance of Sunday, ascribed to Jacob of Serug) (fols.
                     3r-24va)
 II) Taʾammǝra Qʷǝrbān “Miracles of the Eucharist”: 12 miracles
                     (fols. 24vb-40vb)
 
 Additio 1.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">

                     <incipit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </explicit>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <note>Text I concludes with a subscriptio (<locus target="#24va">24va</locus>).</note>
                     <note>Text II concludes with three subscriptiones (<locus from="40vb" to="41ra">40vb-41ra</locus>).</note>
                     <note>Miracles are not numbered.</note>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
