                        Scribe: Mǝṣlalä ʾIyasus. Mǝṣlalä
                        ʾIyasus is mentioned as the scribe in the subscriptiones on <locus target="#24va">24va</locus> and 40vb. He is said “beloved of blatta
                           Kasa”.<date>18th century (?)</date>
