                           <item>
                              <abbr>ለዓ፡ ዓለ፡ አሜን፡</abbr> for <expan>ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን፡ </expan> (<locus target="#34vb">34vb</locus>, 36va, 37rb, 38vb-39ra)</item>
