               <provenance>Walda Śǝllāse is mentioned as the donor in
                     Additio 1. His name is also written in the supplication formulas (e.g., 3r, 29vb, 34vb, 40vb). He is said blatta Kasa on 40vb. His father Za-Walda Māryām Gabra Masqal and his
                     mother Wälätta Muse are mentioned in the subscriptiones on 24va and 40vb.</provenance></history>
